            <div class="single-post indienova-single-post fr-view">
                <h4>快速介绍</h4><p>本周锈湖开发组新作<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/909080/Cube_Escape_Paradox/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《方块逃脱：悖论（Cube Escape: Paradox）》</a>来啦！！</p><p>看着眼熟的也有很多：类 Shelter 游戏<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/911510/Paws_and_Soul/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Paws and Soul</a>、<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/566090/The_Bards_Tale_IV_Barrows_Deep/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《冰城传奇4：深度挖掘》</a>、腾讯自研吃鸡游戏<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/755790/Ring_of_Elysium/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《无限法则（Ring of Elysium）》</a>、星际探索游戏<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/271260/Star_Control_Origins/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《行星控制:起源（Star Control: Origins）》</a>、免费像素益智游戏<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/937930/Elle/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Elle</a>。</p><h4>Speed Brawl 狂飙乱斗</h4><p>关键词：动作、卷轴格斗</p><p>发售日期：9月18日</p><p>与月球入侵者对抗了将近十年之后，人类终于获得了胜利。工业革命随之到来，人们解放了双手，生活变得更加安逸，但也越来越无聊。为了给大家的生活带来点儿刺激，极限运动 Speed Brawl 出现！成为最灵敏、最勇敢的战士，和敌人来一场畅快淋漓的战斗吧！</p><p>本作支持多人在线&amp;本地联机，暂无中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Speed Brawl1 mini.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9419" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Speed Brawl2 mini.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9420" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/468670/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;" __idm_id__="889128961"></iframe></p><h4>The Gardens Between 花园之间</h4><p>关键词：冒险、解谜</p><p>发售日期：9月20日</p><p>一对最好的朋友 Arina 和 Frendt 突然来到了一个个梦幻般的岛屿花园，里面充满着他们童年时代的小记忆。他们一起踏上了一段情感之旅，探讨了友谊的重要性：他们创造的回忆，必须放弃的东西，以及永远不会遗忘的东西。本作支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/The Gardens Between1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9421" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/The Gardens Between2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9422" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/The Gardens Between3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9423" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/600990/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Wizards Tourney</h4><p>关键词：本地多人、休闲、欢乐</p><p>发售日期：9月21日</p><p>绿光还在的时期通过的作品。和朋友们一起玩，在各种小游戏中争做最棒的巫师！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Wizards Tourney.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9465" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/725110/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Blind</h4><p>关键词：VR、黑白、冒险</p><p>发售日期：9月18日</p><p>这款游戏的画面不禁让我想到09年的老独立游戏 <a href="https://kgeisler.itch.io/devils-tuning-fork" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Devil's Tuning Fork</a> （魔鬼的音叉），一款通过敲击音叉来获得视野、进而探路的解谜游戏。这款 VR 游戏 Blind 则是主角失去视力，需要敲击手杖，通过回声来感受世界。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Blind1 mini.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9440" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Blind2.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9441" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Blind3.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9442" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/406860/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Underhero</h4><p>关键词：冒险、平台、RPG</p><p>发售日期：9月20日</p><p>勇者如果没能拯救世界会怎样？Underhero 就是一个这样被魔王统治的世界。但是好在我们还能再来一次冒险！活用你的躲闪和攻击，成为新的英雄吧！万一路上碰到太难的敌人怎么办？贿赂它们！如何对那些怪物致命一击？跟着 BGM 的节奏！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Underhero-1.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9462" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Underhero2.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9463" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Underhero3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9464" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/573320/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>CHANGE: A Homeless Survival Experience</h4><p>关键词：策略、点击</p><p>发售日期：9月20日（Early Access）</p><p>那些无家可归的人过着怎样的生活，又怎样维生呢？在这款游戏中，你将扮演一名流浪汉，面对他们日常中的问题。食物怎么储藏？有那些地方比较适合睡觉？被店员和警察轰走是一种怎样的辛酸？游戏将捐赠20%的利润给慈善机构来真正地帮助这些无家可归的人。游戏暂不支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/CHANGE2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9466" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/CHANGE1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9467" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/CHANGE3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9468" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/926140/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>太吾绘卷</h4><p>关键词：武侠、策略、沙盒</p><p>发售日期：9月21日（Early Access）</p><p>本作是由站内会员 <a href="https://indienova.com/u/conchship" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Conchship</a> 开发的武侠题材独立游戏。</p><p>玩家需要扮演神秘的“太吾氏传人”，还将以不同的处世立场——或善、或恶、或中庸——投身于纷繁复杂的江湖之中。你不仅可以拜访世界各地的武林门派，学习种类繁多的功法绝艺；还可以与人义结金兰，或结下血海深仇；不仅可以兴建自己的村庄，经营各种产业；还可以与自己的挚爱生儿育女，缘定三生；直到你终于面对太吾氏的宿敌，决定世界的命运！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/1.png" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9429" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/3.png" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9430" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/4-1.png" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9432" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/838350/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>60 Parsecs!</h4><p>关键词：策略、搞笑</p><p>发售日期：9月19日</p><p>空间站爆炸了！宇航员们必须得赶快撤离，能否保住全员的性命就靠你了！赶在核弹之前带着队员和补给登上火箭，你只有60秒！游戏支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/60 Parsecs-1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9443" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/60 Parsecs-2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9444" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/60 Parsecs-3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9445" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/646270/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe><br></p><h4>Verlet Swing</h4><p>关键词：动作、迷幻</p><p>发售日期：9月18日</p><p>被各路主播玩坏的<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/582550/Passpartout_The_Starving_Artist/?curator_clanid=33430916" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">《饥饿艺术家（Passpartout: The Starving Artist）》</a>开发组 Flamebait Games 的新作 Verlet Swing 要发售啦！</p><p>在各种古怪的空间中穿梭摆荡，通过100个精心规划的关卡，沉迷于这个狂热的世界吧！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Verlet Swing1 mini.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9434" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Verlet Swing2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9435" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/Verlet Swing3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9436" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/811870/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>My Brother Rabbit</h4><p>关键词：解谜、点击、可爱</p><p>发售日期：9月22日</p><p>待在病床上的时光总是漫长而无趣的，甚至有时候充满痛苦。这款游戏讲述了一位哥哥为卧病在床的妹妹排遣忧郁的故事，孩子们在病魔的残酷现实中用想象力开拓出一片梦幻的世界。游戏支持中文。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/My Brother Rabbit1.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9437" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/My Brother Rabbit2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9438" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2018/9/My Brother Rabbit3.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" data-id="9439" data-result="success" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/855640/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p>
            </div>
        </article>
